      <section id="import-auto-id2056177">
       <title>
Environmental Investigation
       </title>
       <para id="import-auto-id2107035">
        <emphasis effect="bold">
Brief
        </emphasis>
– you are going to investigate the number of grass plants growing on the
lawns of the north side and the south side of South High.
       </para>
       <para id="import-auto-id2107043">
        <emphasis effect="bold">
Investigate
        </emphasis>
– design your investigation.
       </para>
       <para id="import-auto-id2056006">
Your method must be fair, reliable, precise, valid and accurate.
       </para>
       <para id="import-auto-id2056008">
You should record your results in an appropriate table.
       </para>
       <para id="import-auto-id2056010">
        <emphasis effect="bold">
Write up
        </emphasis>
– write up your investigation.
       </para>
       <para id="import-auto-id2070260">
Use the following headings –
       </para>
       <list id="import-auto-id2070262" list-type="bulleted">
        <item>
Hypothesis
        </item>
        <item>
Method
        </item>
        <item>
Justification
        </item>
        <item>
Results
        </item>
        <item>
Analysis
        </item>
        <item>
Evaluation
        </item>
